{"QUIXOTIC":[{"def":"Like Don Quixote; romantic to extravagance; absurdly chivalric; apt to be deluded.","pos":""}],"QUIXOTICALLY":[{"def":"In a quixotic way.","pos":""}],"QUIXOTISM":[{"def":"That form of delusion which leads to extravagant and absurd undertakings or sacrifices in obedience to a morbidly romantic ideal of duty or honor, as illustrated by the exploits of Don Quixote in knight-errantry.","pos":""}],"QUIXOTRY":[{"def":"Quixotism; visionary schemes.","pos":""}]}